## BOOKING FLOW (complete)
1. DoctorListing → DoctorProfile (wire:navigate)
2. BookAppointment step 1: type (in_person | teleconsultation)
3. Step 2: date picker → updatedSelectedDate() clears slot
4. Step 3: slot picker from #[Computed] slots() — excludes booked
5. Step 4: reason, review summary
6. submitBooking() → AppointmentService::book() → appointment(pending,unpaid)
7. $this->dispatch('appointment-booked') → redirect to Checkout
8. Checkout: PayMongo payment intent or source
9. Webhook: payment.paid → ConfirmAppointmentListener → CreateZoomMeetingJob
10. #[On('payment-confirmed')] updates UI, patient notified
11. Doctor confirms (teleconsult already confirmed by payment)
12. 15 min before → reminder notification (wire:poll or Pusher)
13. Post-visit → doctor marks complete → adds MedicalRecord

