- AppointmentConfirmed → [NotifyPatientConfirmed]
- AppointmentCancelled → [NotifyPatientCancellation, DeleteZoomMeetingJob::dispatch()]

Artisan Commands:
- appointments:send-reminders — fire SendAppointmentReminderJob for upcoming
- appointments:mark-no-show — auto-mark missed past appointments
- payments:check-pending — re-query PayMongo for stuck pending payments

